<span id="Options"></span>
== Опции ==

The color of a subtraction element can follow the style of [[Draft_ToggleConstructionMode|Draft construction]] elements, by activating the appropriate option in the [[Arch_Preferences|Arch Preferences]], in the menu {{MenuCommand|Edit → Preferences → BIM → General Settings → Apply Draft construction style to subcomponents}}.

The [[Draft_ToggleConstructionMode|Draft construction]] style can be set in the [[Draft_Preferences|Draft Preferences]], in the menu {{MenuCommand|Preferences → Draft → General}}.


